                                    "explanation": {
                                        "en": "Multiply by $\\frac{\\sqrt{6}}{\\sqrt{6}}$.",
                                        "uz": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{6}}{\\sqrt{6}}$ ga ko'paytiring.",
                                        "ru": "Умножьте на $\\frac{\\sqrt{6}}{\\sqrt{6}}$."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
